text: Last Pair Out () is a 1956 Swedish drama movie directed by Alf Sjöberg and was written by Ingmar Bergman. It stars Eva Dahlbeck, Harriet Andersson, Bibi Andersson, Björn Bjelfvenstam, Jarl Kulle, Hugo Björne, Jan-Olof Strandberg, Jullan Kindahl. ==Cast== * Eva Dahlbeck – Susanna Dahlin * Harriet Andersson – Anita * Bibi Andersson – Kerstin * Björn Bjelfvenstam – Bo Dahlin * Jarl Kulle – Dr. Farell * Olof Widgren – Hans Dahlin * Aino Taube – Kerstin's mother * Hugo Björne – Professor Jacobi * Jan-Olof Strandberg – Claes Berg * Märta Arbin – Grandmother * Jullan Kindahl – Alma ==Other websites== * Category:1956 drama movies Category:Swedish drama movies Category:Movies directed by Alf Sjöberg
title: Last Pair Out
